"title": "8624: worship, reasons for",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8624",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The supreme reason for human existence is to worship God for his love, greatness and saving deeds.</p>\n<h2>To worship is a divine command</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:10\">MAT 4:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:8\">LUK 4:8</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:13\">DEU 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:25\">EXO 23:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:36\">2KI 17:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:23\">PSA 22:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:2\">PSA 29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:26\">PSA 68:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps113:1\">PSA 113:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps117:1\">PSA 117:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:11-Ps148:13\">PSA 148:11–148:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:6\">PSA 150:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:8\">1TI 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:7\">REV 14:7</a></p>\n<h2>God's people are to be a worshipping people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5-Exod19:6\">EXO 19:5–19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:1-Ps105:6\">PSA 105:1–105:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:21\">ISA 43:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5-Rev1:6\">REV 1:5–1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Worship is the response of God's people</h2>\n<h3>To God's love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:31\">EXO 4:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:7\">DEU 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:10-Deut26:11\">DEU 26:10–26:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:3\">2CH 7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:6-Ps95:7\">PSA 95:6–95:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps117:1-Ps117:2\">PSA 117:1–117:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:2\">PSA 138:2</a></p>\n<h3>To God's holy presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:29</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:8-Ps96:9\">PSA 96:8–96:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:10\">EXO 33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:3\">LEV 10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:13-Josh5:15\">JOS 5:13–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:2\">PSA 29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:5\">PSA 99:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:8\">REV 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:4\">REV 15:4</a></p>\n<h3>To God's greatness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:1-Ps95:3\">PSA 95:1–95:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:12\">EXO 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:27-Ps22:28\">PSA 22:27–22:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:1-Ps66:4\">PSA 66:1–66:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:1-Ps96:3\">PSA 96:1–96:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3-Rev15:4\">REV 15:3–15:4</a></p>\n<h2>To the deeds of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:20\">GEN 8:20</a></strong> <em>Noah's response to God's deliverance from the flood.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:7\">GEN 12:7</a> <em>God's promise of an inheritance to Abraham</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:29-Exod4:31\">EXO 4:29–4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:27\">EXO 12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:1\">EXO 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:20\">EXO 15:20</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:10-Ezra3:11\">EZR 3:10–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:21\">ISA 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:28\">DAN 3:28</a> <em>God's deliverance of Daniel in Babylon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:7-Matt9:8\">MAT 9:7–9:8</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:12\">MRK 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:25-Luke5:26\">LUK 5:25–5:26</a> <em>the healing of the paralytic</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:8\">ACT 3:8</a> <em>the healing of the crippled beggar</em></p>\n<h3>To the fear of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:23\">PSA 22:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28\">HEB 12:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:11\">PSA 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:2\">ACT 10:2</a></p>",
